HEADWORD: Predorsal
<hw>Pre*dor"sal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated in front of the back; immediately in front, or on the
ventral side the dorsal part of the vertebral column.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

